OL,7,FTobias Ellwood, the chair of
OL,8,FParliament's Defence Select
OL,9,FCommittee, has apologised for a video
OL,10,Fin which he claimed Afghanistan had
OL,11,Fbeen "transformed" under the Taliban.
OL,13,FIn the clip posted to Twitter from
OL,14,FAfghanistan on Monday, Mr Ellwood, a
OL,15,Fformer defence minister, said
OL,16,Fcorruption was falling and security
OL,17,Fhad "vastly improved" ` with no
OL,18,Freference to the harsh restrictions
OL,19,Fre-imposed by the Taliban on rights
OL,20,Ffor women and girls.
OL,3,CTory MP Tobias Ellwood apologises for
OL,4,Cpraising Afghanistan under Taliban
